<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/page_actions.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/page_actions.tpl) -->
    <!--Content-Begin-->
    <article>
            <h1>ECO-design og energimærkning</h1>
      <summary>
        <p>
                      
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl) -->

Sikkerhedsstyrelsen skal fra 1. august 2018 udføre markedsovervågning med eco-design og energimærkning af elprodukter for Energistyrelsen. Det praktiske arbejde med kontrollen udføres af Sekretariatet for Ecodesign og Energimærkning, som hidtil har løst opgaven for Energistyrelsen. 
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/eztext.tpl) -->
                            </p>
      </summary>
      <div class="pull-right social-icons">
<!-- START: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl) -->
<a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://sik.dk/Virksomhed/Produktsikkerhed-for-fagfolk/Markedsovervaagning-af-nye-omraader/ECO-design-og-energimaerkning" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-facebook-square facebook-brand"></i></a>
<a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=https://sik.dk/Virksomhed/Produktsikkerhed-for-fagfolk/Markedsovervaagning-af-nye-omraader/ECO-design-og-energimaerkning" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-twitter-square twitter-brand"></i></a>
<a href="https://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https://sik.dk/Virksomhed/Produktsikkerhed-for-fagfolk/Markedsovervaagning-af-nye-omraader/ECO-design-og-energimaerkning" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-pinterest-square pinterest-brand"></i></a>
<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&amp;url=https://sik.dk/Virksomhed/Produktsikkerhed-for-fagfolk/Markedsovervaagning-af-nye-omraader/ECO-design-og-energimaerkning" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-linkedin-square linkedin-brand"></i></a>
<a href="mailto:?subject=ECO-design og energimærkning&body=https://sik.dk/Virksomhed/Produktsikkerhed-for-fagfolk/Markedsovervaagning-af-nye-omraader/ECO-design-og-energimaerkning" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-envelope-o mail-brand"></i></a>

<!-- STOP: including template: extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl (extension/sikkerhedsstyrelsen/design/design_2013/templates/partials/body/social_icons.tpl) -->
</div>
      <br>
      <hr>
        
              
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->


<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Anmeld det til sekretariatet, hvis du har mistanke om, at et produkt ikke overholder reglerne:&nbsp;
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
<a href="mailto:sekretariat@eco-energimaerke.dk" target="_self">sekretariat@eco-energimaerke.dk</a>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Eco-design</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Kravene til eco-design er reguleret ved EU-direktiv 2009/125/EF, der fastsætter mindstekrav bl.a. til energieffektivitet for energiforbrugende produkter. I dansk lovgivning findes kravene i lovbekendtgørelse 1068/15/2010 og bekendtgørelse nr. 1274/19/2010.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Energistyrelsen har fortsat det overordnede ansvar for reglerne omkring miljøvenligt design af energirelaterede produkter.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Sikkerhedsstyrelsen kontrollerer, at produkter lever op til de fastsatte regler og træffer afgørelser, hvis et produkt ikke lever op til kravene. Overtrædelser kan føre til påbud, forbud eller evt. politianmeldelse. Der kan også videregives oplysninger om overtrædelser til andre danske eller udenlandske myndigheder.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Se mere om kravene til eco-design hos 
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
<a href="https://ens.dk/ansvarsomraader/energikrav-til-produkter/om-energikrav" target="_blank">Energistyrelsen</a>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
<b>Energimærkning</b>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/strong.tpl) -->
</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Kravene til energimærkning af energirelaterede produkter er reguleret ved EU-forordning 2017/1369, lov nr. 455 af 18. maj 2011 om energimærkning af energirelaterede produkter og bekendtgørelse nr. 1026 af 4. november 2011 om energimærkning af energirelaterede produkter.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Energistyrelsen har fortsat det overordnede ansvar for energimærkning af energirelaterede produkter. Sikkerhedsstyrelsen fører tilsyn med, at produkterne overholder de fastsatte regler og træffer afgørelser, hvis et produkt ikke lever op til kravene. Overtrædelser kan føre til påbud eller forbud, og oplysninger om overtrædelser kan videregives til andre danske eller udenlandske myndigheder.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->
<p>Se mere om energikrav og energimærkning hos 
<!-- START: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
<a href="https://ens.dk/ansvarsomraader/energikrav-til-produkter/om-energikrav" target="_blank">Energistyrelsen</a>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/link.tpl) -->
.</p>
<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltags/paragraph.tpl) -->

<!-- STOP: including template: design/standard/templates/content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl (design:content/datatype/view/ezxmltext.tpl) -->
      
      
